summary: I HAVE A "KEYLESS START SYSTEM PROBLEM" MESSAGE ON  SINCE THE CAR IS MORE THAN 37,000 MILES.  TRIED CHANGING BATTERY BUT IT DID NOT FIX THE PROBLEM.  IT DOES NOT SEEM TO AFFECT THE DRIVING.   AT 61,000 MILES THE DEALER RESET THE CODE BUT AFTER ONE DAY, THE MESSAGE CAME BACK.  THIS ISSUE DISABLED THE AUTOLOCK FEATURE AS YOU WALK AWAY.  NOT SURE WHAT ELSE IS BEING DISABLED BY THIS.
